				"Nombre 2.0",
				"Recepci\u00f3n 2.0",
				"Jugar a baloncesto es diversi\u00f3n.",
				"Tome por favor una bebida fresca.",
				"This is an unlocalized hook message.",
				"This is an unlocalized portlet message.",
